            <h3>why Dolphin:</h3>

            <ul>
              <li>
                Dolphin Foundation village is a rescue center for abandoned and
                orphaned babies, offering women education, micro-business
                opportunities and life skills, reuniting children with extended
                families and renewing hope to AIDs widows
              </li>
              <li>
                A Rescue Center for Orphaned, Abandoned, and At-Risk babies in
                Kampala, Uganda. MAP, a mothers against poverty program. Daycare
                for handicap babies. Save the Moms
              </li>
